## üìä Output Examples

### ‚úÖ No Secrets Detected

```
üîç Scanning 3 file(s) for secrets...
‚úÖ No secrets detected. Safe to commit.
```

### ‚ùå Secrets Detected

```
üîç Scanning 2 file(s) for secrets...

‚ùå Secrets detected:
   üìÑ config.env:5 [Password] -> pass****
      Code: password=MySecret123

   üìÑ api.py:12 [API Key] -> AKIA****
      Code: aws_access_key = "AKIAIOSFODNN7EXAMPLE"

üö´ Found 2 secret(s). Please remove them before committing.
```

